P_HTM[1916]='*83. Hetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya  sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto ca nahetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[1917]='*Nahetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[1918]='*Hetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttañca nahetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttañca dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1919]='*84. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe nava, nissaye nava, upanissaye nava, purejāte nava, āsevane nava, kamme  nava, vipāke ekaṃ, āhāre nava, indriye nava, jhāne nava, magge nava, sampayutte nava, vippayutte nava, atthiyā nava, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate nava (anulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1920]='*Nahetu-naadhipatipaccayā*';
P_HTM[1921]='*85. Nahetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (1)*';
P_HTM[1922]='*86. Hetuṃ dukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu dukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1923]='*87. Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ (paccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1924]='*Hetupaccayā naadhipatiyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomapaccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1925]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyānulomaṃ).*';
