P_HTM[1939]='*93. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava, naadhipatiyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1940]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomapaccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1941]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyānulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1942]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[1943]='*3. Adukkhamasukhāyavedanāyasampayuttapadaṃ*';
