P_HTM[1953]='*97. Hetuṃ adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya sampayutto dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[1954]='*98. Nahetuyā dve, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyaṃ).*';
