P_HTM[2088]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[2089]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[2090]='*(Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
