P_HTM[2137]='*167. Hetuṃ  anupādinnupādāniyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu anupādinnupādāniyo dhammo uppajjati naārammaṇapaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[2138]='*Nahetuṃ anupādinnupādāniyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu anupādinnupādāniyo dhammo uppajjati naārammaṇapaccayā. (1)*';
