P_HTM[3623]='*25. Hetusampayuttaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetusampayutto kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3624]='*26. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3625]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[3626]='*27. Naadhipatiyā ekaṃ, napurejāte ekaṃ, napacchājāte ekaṃ, naāsevane ekaṃ, nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke ekaṃ, navippayutte ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3627]='*Hetupaccayā naadhipatiyā ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3628]='*Naadhipatipaccayā hetuyā ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3629]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3630]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3631]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3632]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3633]='*28. Hetusampayutto  kusalo dhammo hetusampayuttassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3634]='*Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā ekaṃ, anantare ekaṃ, samanantare ekaṃ…pe… kamme ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
