P_HTM[3636]='*29. Hetusampayutto  kusalo dhammo hetusampayuttassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo.*';
P_HTM[3637]='*30. Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3638]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3639]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
