P_HTM[3707]='*47. Hetuñceva sahetukañca kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva sahetuko ca kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[3708]='*Sahetukañceva na ca hetuṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sahetuko ceva na ca hetu kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
