P_HTM[3755]='*63. Hetuñceva sahetukañca abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva sahetuko ca abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3756]='*64. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… kamme nava, vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3757]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[3758]='*65. Hetuñceva sahetukañca abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva sahetuko ca abyākato dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3759]='*66. Naadhipatiyā  nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3760]='*Hetupaccayā  naadhipatiyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3761]='*Naadhipatipaccayā hetuyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3762]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāro sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3763]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3764]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3765]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3766]='*67. Hetu  ceva sahetuko ca abyākato dhammo hetussa ceva sahetukassa ca abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3767]='*68. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe nava, nissaye nava, upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, vipāke nava, āhāre tīṇi…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3768]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3769]='*69. Hetu ceva sahetuko ca abyākato dhammo hetussa ceva sahetukassa ca abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3770]='*70. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3771]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3772]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3773]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3774]='*Hetusahetukadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3775]='*5-1. Hetuhetusampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3776]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
