P_HTM[3779]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3780]='*71. Hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuñceva  hetusampayuttañca kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetusampayutto ceva na ca hetu kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3781]='*72. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3782]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[3783]='*73. Hetuñceva  hetusampayuttañca kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca kusalo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3784]='*74. Naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
