P_HTM[3786]='*Adhipatipaccayā hetuyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3787]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3788]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3789]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3790]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3791]='*75. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca kusalo dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3792]='*76. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava…pe… āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3793]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3794]='*77. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca kusalo dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca kusalassa  dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3795]='*78. Nahetuyā  nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3796]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3797]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3798]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
