P_HTM[3806]='*81. Hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3807]='*82. Naadhipatiyā  nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3808]='*Hetupaccayā  naadhipatiyā tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3809]='*Naadhipatipaccayā hetuyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3810]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3811]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3812]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3813]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3814]='*83. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca akusalo dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3815]='*Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3816]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3817]='*84. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca akusalo dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3818]='*85. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3819]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3820]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3821]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3822]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3823]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3824]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3825]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3826]='*86. Hetuñceva  hetusampayuttañca abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3827]='*Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… kamme nava, vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3828]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[3829]='*87. Hetuñceva hetusampayuttañca abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca abyākato dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3830]='*88. Naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3831]='*Hetupaccayā  naadhipatiyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3832]='*Naadhipatipaccayā  hetuyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3833]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3834]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3835]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3836]='*Hetupaccayādi*';
P_HTM[3837]='*89. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca abyākato dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3838]='*90. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, vipāke nava, āhāre tīṇi, indriye nava, jhāne tīṇi, magge sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3839]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3840]='*91. Hetu ceva hetusampayutto ca abyākato dhammo hetussa ceva hetusampayuttassa ca abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3841]='*92. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3842]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3843]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3844]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3845]='*Hetuhetusampayuttadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3846]='*6-1. Nahetusahetukaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3847]='*1-2. Kusalākusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3848]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3849]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3850]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3851]='*93. Nahetuṃ  sahetukaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu sahetuko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3852]='*94. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ (sabbattha ekaṃ), avigate ekaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3853]='*Naadhipatiyā ekaṃ, napurejāte ekaṃ…pe… navipāke ekaṃ, navippayutte  ekaṃ (pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3854]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3855]='*95. Nahetuṃ sahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu sahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3856]='*96. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ (sabbattha ekaṃ), avigate ekaṃ. (Hetupaccayo natthi. Pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ, pañhāvārepi imesaṃ tiṇṇannaṃ hetupaccayo natthi.)*';
P_HTM[3857]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3858]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3859]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3860]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3861]='*97. Nahetuṃ  sahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu sahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuṃ sahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nahetuṃ sahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu sahetuko abyākato ca nahetu ahetuko abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[3862]='*Nahetuṃ ahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[3863]='*Nahetuṃ  sahetukaṃ abyākatañca nahetuṃ ahetukaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu  sahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3864]='*98. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… purejāte āsevane dve, kamme nava, vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3865]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3866]='*99. Nahetuṃ ahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3867]='*100. Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava, naanantare tīṇi, nasamanantare  tīṇi, naaññamaññe tīṇi, naupanissaye tīṇi, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme dve, navipāke pañca, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte dve, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3868]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3869]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3870]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3871]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3872]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3873]='*Ārammaṇapaccayo*';
P_HTM[3874]='*101. Nahetu sahetuko abyākato dhammo nahetussa sahetukassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3875]='*102. Ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā cattāri, anantare cattāri, samanantare cattāri, sahajāte satta, aññamaññe cha, nissaye  satta, upanissaye  cattāri, purejāte dve, pacchājāte dve, āsevane dve, kamme cattāri, vipāke cattāri, āhāre cattāri, indriye cattāri, jhāne cattāri, magge tīṇi, sampayutte dve, vippayutte tīṇi, atthiyā satta, natthiyā cattāri, vigate cattāri, avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3876]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3877]='*103. Nahetu sahetuko abyākato dhammo nahetussa sahetukassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena  paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3878]='*104. Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3879]='*Ārammaṇapaccayā nahetuyā cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3880]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3881]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3882]='*Nahetusahetukadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3883]='*Hetugocchakaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3884]='*7-1. Sappaccayaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3885]='*1-2. Kusalākusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3886]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3887]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3888]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3889]='*1. Sappaccayaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaccayo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3890]='*2. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3891]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[3892]='*3. Sappaccayaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaccayo kusalo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3893]='*4. Naadhipatiyā  ekaṃ, napurejāte ekaṃ, napacchājāte ekaṃ, naāsevane ekaṃ, nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke ekaṃ, navippayutte ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3894]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3895]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3896]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3897]='*5. Sappaccayo kusalo dhammo sappaccayassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3898]='*6. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3899]='*7. Sappaccayaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaccayo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3900]='*8. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ. (Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3901]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3902]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3903]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3904]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3905]='*9. Sappaccayaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaccayo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3906]='*10. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3907]='*Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā ekaṃ (sabbattha ekaṃ, saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3908]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3909]='*Hetupaccayādi*';
P_HTM[3910]='*11. Sappaccayo abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3911]='*Sappaccayo abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3912]='*Appaccayo  abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3913]='*Sappaccayo  abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3914]='*Appaccayo abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇūpanissayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3915]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā dve, anantare ekaṃ…pe… nissaye ekaṃ, upanissaye dve, purejāte ekaṃ, pacchājāte ekaṃ, (sabbattha ekaṃ), avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3916]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3917]='*12. Sappaccayo abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa  dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo.*';
P_HTM[3918]='*Appaccayo abyākato dhammo sappaccayassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3919]='*13. Nahetuyā dve, naārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3920]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3921]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3922]='*Sappaccayadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3923]='*8-1. Saṅkhataduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3924]='*14. Saṅkhataṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saṅkhato kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ. Sappaccayasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3925]='*Saṅkhatadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3926]='*9-1. Sanidassanaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3927]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3928]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3929]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3930]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3931]='*15. Anidassanaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anidassano kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3932]='*16. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ. (Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3933]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3934]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3935]='*17. Anidassanaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anidassano akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3936]='*18. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ. (Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3937]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3938]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3939]='*19. Anidassanaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anidassano abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3940]='*20. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā tīṇi…pe… avigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3941]='*Nahetuyā tīṇi (sabbattha tīṇi), nakamme tīṇi, navipāke tīṇi, naāhāre tīṇi…pe… novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3942]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[3943]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3944]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3945]='*Hetupaccayādi*';
P_HTM[3946]='*21. Anidassano  abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[3947]='*Sanidassano  abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3948]='*Anidassano abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3949]='*Sanidassano abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇādhipati. (1)*';
P_HTM[3950]='*Anidassano abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇādhipati, sahajātādhipati. Anidassano abyākato dhammo sanidassanassa abyākatassa ca anidassanassa abyākatassa ca dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – sahajātādhipati. (2)*';
P_HTM[3951]='*Sanidassano  abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo – pakatūpanissayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[3952]='*Anidassano abyākato dhammo anidassanassa abyākatassa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇūpanissayo, anantarūpanissayo, pakatūpanissayo…pe…. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3953]='*22. Purejāte tīṇi, pacchājāte tīṇi, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme  tīṇi, vipāke tīṇi, (sabbattha tīṇi) sampayutte ekaṃ, vippayutte tīṇi, atthiyā pañca, natthiyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate pañca. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3954]='*Sanidassanadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3955]='*(Appaccayampi asaṅkhatampi sanidassanampi na labbhati.)*';
P_HTM[3956]='*10-1. Sappaṭighaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3957]='*1-2. Kusalākusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3958]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3959]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3960]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3961]='*23. Appaṭighaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appaṭigho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3962]='*24. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… vippayutte ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3963]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3964]='*25. Appaṭighaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appaṭigho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3965]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3966]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3967]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3968]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3969]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3970]='*26. Sappaṭighaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaṭigho abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sappaṭighaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appaṭigho abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sappaṭighaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaṭigho abyākato ca appaṭigho abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā… nava.*';
P_HTM[3971]='*Appaṭighaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appaṭigho abyākato dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3972]='*27. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā nava…pe… aññamaññe cha, nissaye nava, upanissaye ekaṃ, purejāte āsevane ekaṃ, kamme nava, vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3973]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3974]='*28. Sappaṭighaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappaṭigho abyākato dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3975]='*29. Nahetuyā nava…pe… novigate nava (sabbattha nava, saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3976]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[3977]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3978]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3979]='*30. Appaṭigho abyākato dhammo appaṭighassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3980]='*31. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare ekaṃ, samanantare ekaṃ, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe cha, nissaye nava, upanissaye dve, purejāte tīṇi, pacchājāte  tīṇi, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme tīṇi, vipāke tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi, indriye pañca, jhāne tīṇi, magge tīṇi, sampayutte ekaṃ, vippayutte cattāri, atthiyā nava, natthiyā ekaṃ, vigate ekaṃ, avigate nava.*';
P_HTM[3981]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[3982]='*32. Sappaṭigho abyākato dhammo sappaṭighassa abyākatassa dhammassa sahajātapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3983]='*33. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3984]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3985]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3986]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[3987]='*Sappaṭighadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[3988]='*11-1. Rūpīduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[3989]='*1-2. Kusalākusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3990]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3991]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[3992]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[3993]='*34. Arūpiṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca arūpī kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3994]='*35. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3995]='*36. Arūpiṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca arūpī akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3996]='*37. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[3997]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[3998]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[3999]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4000]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayā*';
P_HTM[4001]='*38. Rūpiṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca rūpī abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4002]='*Arūpiṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca arūpī abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4003]='*Rūpiṃ abyākatañca arūpiṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca rūpī abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4004]='*Rūpiṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca arūpī abyākato dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4005]='*39. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā pañca, anantare tīṇi, samanantare tīṇi…pe… aññamaññe cha…pe… purejāte ekaṃ, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme nava, vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4006]='*40. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… nakamme dve, navipāke pañca, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne dve, namagge nava, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte  dve, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4007]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4008]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4009]='*41. Arūpī  abyākato dhammo arūpissa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4010]='*42. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare ekaṃ, samanantare ekaṃ, sahajāte satta, aññamaññe cha, nissaye satta, upanissaye dve, purejāte ekaṃ, pacchājāte ekaṃ, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme tīṇi, vipāke tīṇi, āhāre cattāri, indriye cha, jhāne tīṇi, magge tīṇi, sampayutte ekaṃ, vippayutte dve…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4011]='*Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4012]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4013]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4014]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4015]='*Rūpīdukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4016]='*11-1. Lokiyaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4017]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4018]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4019]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4020]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4021]='*43. Lokiyaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokiyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4022]='*Lokuttaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokuttaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4023]='*Lokiyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokiyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4024]='*Lokuttaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokuttaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4025]='*44. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā dve…pe… kamme dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4026]='*45. Naadhipatiyā dve…pe… naāsevane ekaṃ…pe… navippayutte dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4027]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4028]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4029]='*Hetupaccayādi*';
P_HTM[4030]='*46. Lokiyo  kusalo dhammo lokiyassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4031]='*Lokuttaro  kusalo dhammo lokuttarassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4032]='*Lokiyo kusalo dhammo lokiyassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4033]='*Lokuttaro kusalo dhammo lokiyassa kusalassa  dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4034]='*Lokiyo kusalo dhammo lokiyassa kusalassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇādhipati, sahajātādhipati. (1)*';
P_HTM[4035]='*Lokuttaro kusalo dhammo lokuttarassa kusalassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – sahajātādhipati. Lokuttaro kusalo dhammo lokiyassa kusalassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo – ārammaṇādhipati. (2) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4036]='*47. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare dve, samanantare dve, sahajāte dve…pe… upanissaye cattāri, āsevane dve, kamme dve, āhāre dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4037]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4038]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4039]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4040]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4041]='*48. Lokiyaṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokiyo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4042]='*49. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ, sahajātavāropi…pe… pañhāvāropi sabbattha sadisā).*';
P_HTM[4043]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4044]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4045]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4046]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4047]='*50. Lokiyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokiyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4048]='*Lokuttaraṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca lokuttaro  abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4049]='*Lokiyaṃ  abyākatañca lokuttaraṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca lokiyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4050]='*51. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe… āsevane ekaṃ, kamme pañca, vipāke pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4051]='*52. Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā dve…pe… napurejāte cattāri, napacchājāte pañca…pe… nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke ekaṃ, naāhāre ekaṃ…pe… namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte dve, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4052]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4053]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4054]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4055]='*53. Lokiyo abyākato dhammo lokiyassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4056]='*Lokuttaro abyākato dhammo lokuttarassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4057]='*54. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā cattāri, anantare cattāri, sahajāte pañca, aññamaññe dve, nissaye satta, upanissaye cattāri, purejāte dve, pacchājāte dve, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme cattāri, vipāke cattāri, āhāre cattāri…pe… magge cattāri, sampayutte dve, vippayutte  tīṇi, atthiyā satta…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4058]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4059]='*Lokiyadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4060]='*13-1. Kenaciviññeyyaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4061]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4062]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4063]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4064]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4065]='*55. Kenaci  viññeyyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kenaci viññeyyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kenaci viññeyyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kenaci naviññeyyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kenaci viññeyyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kenaci viññeyyo kusalo ca kenaci naviññeyyo kusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4066]='*56. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4067]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4068]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[4069]='*57. Kenaci viññeyyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kenaci viññeyyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4070]='*58. Naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme nava, navipāke nava…pe… navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4071]='*(Sahajātavāropi  paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4072]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4073]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4074]='*59. Kenaci  viññeyyo kusalo dhammo kenaci viññeyyassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4075]='*60. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava, samanantare nava…pe… kamme nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4076]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4077]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4078]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4079]='*(Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ. Kenaci viññeyyaṃ akusalampi kenaci viññeyyaṃ abyākatampi kenaci viññeyyakusalasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4080]='*Kenaciviññeyyadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4081]='*Cūḷantaradukaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4082]='*14-1. Āsavaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4083]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4084]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4085]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4086]='*1. Noāsavaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca noāsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4087]='*2. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… kamme ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4088]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4089]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4090]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4091]='*3. Āsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4092]='*4. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4093]='*Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4094]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi sabbattha vitthāretabbo.)*';
P_HTM[4095]='*5. Āsavo akusalo dhammo āsavassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo.*';
P_HTM[4096]='*6. Hetuyā  satta, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava (majjhe tiṇṇaṃ sahajātādhipati labbhati), anantare nava…pe… upanissaye nava, āsevane  nava, kamme tīṇi…pe… jhāne tīṇi, magge nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4097]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4098]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4099]='*7. Noāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca noāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4100]='*8. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ. (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi paccayavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4101]='*Āsavadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4102]='*15-1. Sāsavaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4103]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4104]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4105]='*9. Sāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4106]='*Anāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anāsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4107]='*10. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4108]='*11. Naadhipatiyā dve…pe… naāsevane ekaṃ…pe… navippayutte dve (saṃkhittaṃ. Paccanīyaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha dve).*';
P_HTM[4109]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4110]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4111]='*12. Sāsavo  kusalo dhammo sāsavassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4112]='*Anāsavo kusalo dhammo anāsavassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4113]='*13. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare dve…pe… nissaye dve, upanissaye cattāri, āsevane dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4114]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4115]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4116]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4117]='*14. Sāsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4118]='*15. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4119]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4120]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4121]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4122]='*16. Sāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4123]='*Anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo abyākato ca anāsavo abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[4124]='*Sāsavaṃ abyākatañca anāsavaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4125]='*17. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… āsevane ekaṃ…pe… vipāke pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4126]='*Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā dve, napurejāte cattāri, napacchājāte naāsevane pañca, nakamme…pe… namagge ekaṃ…pe… navippayutte dve…pe… novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4127]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi sabbattha vitthāretabbo.)*';
P_HTM[4128]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4129]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4130]='*18. Sāsavo  abyākato dhammo sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4131]='*Anāsavo abyākato dhammo anāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4132]='*19. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā anantare samanantare cattāri, sahajāte pañca, aññamaññe dve, nissaye satta, upanissaye cattāri, purejāte pacchājāte dve, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme…pe… magge cattāri, sampayutte dve, vippayutte tīṇi…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4133]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4134]='*Sāsavadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4135]='*16-1. Āsavasampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4136]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4137]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4138]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4139]='*20. Āsavavippayuttaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4140]='*21. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4141]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4142]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4143]='*22. Āsavasampayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavasampayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4144]='*Āsavavippayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavasampayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4145]='*Āsavasampayuttaṃ  akusalañca āsavavippayuttaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavasampayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4146]='*23. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha pañca.)*';
P_HTM[4147]='*Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā pañca, napurejāte pañca…pe… nakamme tīṇi, navipāke pañca, navippayutte pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4148]='*24. Āsavasampayutto akusalo dhammo āsavasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4149]='*Āsavavippayutto  akusalo dhammo āsavasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4150]='*Āsavasampayutto akusalo ca āsavavippayutto akusalo ca dhammā āsavasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4151]='*25. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā ekaṃ, anantare samanantare nava, sahajāte aññamaññe nissaye pañca, upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme āhāre indriye jhāne magge tīṇi, sampayutte pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4152]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4153]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4154]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4155]='*26. Āsavavippayuttaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4156]='*27. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4157]='*Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naārammaṇe ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe… novigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4158]='*28. Āsavavippayutto  abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4159]='*29. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4160]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4161]='*Āsavasampayuttadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4162]='*17-1. Āsavasāsavaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4163]='*1. Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4164]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4165]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4166]='*30. Sāsavañceva  no ca āsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo ceva no ca āsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4167]='*31. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4168]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4169]='*2. Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4170]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4171]='*32. Āsavañceva  sāsavañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva sāsavo ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4172]='*Sāsavañceva no ca āsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo ceva no ca āsavo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4173]='*Āsavañceva sāsavañca akusalañca sāsavañceva no ca āsavaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva sāsavo ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4174]='*33. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4175]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4176]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4177]='*34. Sāsavañceva no ca āsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva sāsavo ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4178]='*35. Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte  nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4179]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4180]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4181]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4182]='*36. Āsavo  ceva sāsavoca akusalo dhammo āsavassa ceva sāsavassa ca akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4183]='*37. Hetuyā satta, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme āhāre indriye jhāne tīṇi, magge sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4184]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[4185]='*38. Āsavo ceva sāsavo ca akusalo dhammo āsavassa ceva sāsavassa ca akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4186]='*39. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4187]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4188]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4189]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4190]='*3. Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4191]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4192]='*40. Sāsavañceva no ca āsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sāsavo ceva no ca āsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4193]='*41. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4194]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4195]='*Āsavasāsavadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4196]='*18-1. Āsavaāsavasampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4197]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4198]='*Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4199]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4200]='*42. Āsavañceva  āsavasampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva āsavasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4201]='*Āsavasampayuttañceva no ca āsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavasampayutto ceva no ca āsavo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4202]='*Āsavañceva āsavasampayuttañca akusalañca āsavasampayuttañceva no ca āsavaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva āsavasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4203]='*43. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4204]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4205]='*Naadhipatipaccayo*';
P_HTM[4206]='*44. Āsavañceva  āsavasampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavo ceva āsavasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati naadhipatipaccayā.*';
P_HTM[4207]='*45. Naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4208]='*(Sahajātavārepi… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha nava.)*';
P_HTM[4209]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4210]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4211]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4212]='*46. Āsavo ceva āsavasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo āsavassa ceva āsavasampayuttassa ca akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4213]='*47. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4214]='*Nahetuyā  nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4215]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4216]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4217]='*(Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4218]='*Āsavaāsavasampayuttadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4219]='*19-1. Āsavavippayuttasāsavaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4220]='*Kusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4221]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4222]='*48. Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto anāsavo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (2) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4223]='*49. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4224]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… pañhāvāropi vitthāretabbo.)*';
P_HTM[4225]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4226]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4227]='*50. Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4228]='*Āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto anāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato ca āsavavippayutto anāsavo abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[4229]='*Āsavavippayuttaṃ  sāsavaṃ abyākatañca āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4230]='*51. Hetuyā  pañca, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… āsevane ekaṃ, kamme pañca, vipāke pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4231]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4232]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4233]='*52. Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4234]='*53. Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā dve  …pe… napurejāte cattāri, napacchājāte naāsevane pañca, nakamme navipāke…pe… namagge ekaṃ…pe… navippayutte dve…pe… novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4235]='*(Sahajātavāropi paccayavāropi nissayavāropi saṃsaṭṭhavāropi sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4236]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4237]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4238]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayā*';
P_HTM[4239]='*54. Āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo.*';
P_HTM[4240]='*Āsavavippayutto  anāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa anāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. Āsavavippayutto anāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. Āsavavippayutto anāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa ca āsavavippayuttassa anāsavassa abyākatassa ca dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[4241]='*Āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4242]='*Āsavavippayutto  anāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa anāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Āsavavippayutto anāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4243]='*55. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā cattāri, anantare cattāri, samanantare cattāri, sahajāte pañca, aññamaññe dve, nissaye satta, upanissaye cattāri, purejāte dve, āsevane ekaṃ, kamme cattāri, vipāke cattāri, āhāre cattāri…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4244]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[4245]='*56. Āsavavippayutto sāsavo abyākato dhammo āsavavippayuttassa sāsavassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo… purejātapaccayena paccayo… pacchājātapaccayena paccayo… āhārapaccayena paccayo… indriyapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4246]='*57. Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4247]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4248]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4249]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4250]='*Āsavavippayuttasāsavadukakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4251]='*Āsavagocchakaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[4252]='*20-1. Saññojanaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4253]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4254]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4255]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4256]='*1. Nosaññojanaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nosaññojano kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4257]='*2. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4258]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4259]='*3. Saññojanaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojano akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Saññojanaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nosaññojano akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Saññojanaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojano akusalo ca nosaññojano akusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4260]='*4. Hetuyā  nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4261]='*Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… nakamme tīṇi…pe… navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4262]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4263]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4264]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4265]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4266]='*5. Saññojano  akusalo dhammo saññojanassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4267]='*6. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre indriye jhāne tīṇi, magge sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4268]='*7. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4269]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4270]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4271]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4272]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4273]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4274]='*8. Nosaññojanaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nosaññojano abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4275]='*9. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4276]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4277]='*21-1. Saññojaniyaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4278]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4279]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4280]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4281]='*10. Saññojaniyaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4282]='*Asaññojaniyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca asaññojaniyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4283]='*11. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4284]='*(Yathā cūḷantaraduke lokiyadukagamanaṃ, evaṃ imampi ñātabbaṃ. Sahajātavāropi…pe… pañhāvāropi vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4285]='*12. Saññojaniyaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4286]='*13. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4287]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4288]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4289]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4290]='*14. Saññojaniyaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4291]='*Asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca asaññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo abyākato ca asaññojaniyo abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[4292]='*Saññojaniyaṃ abyākatañca asaññojaniyaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4293]='*15. Hetuyā  pañca, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4294]='*Cūḷantaraduke lokiyadukasadisaṃ. (Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4295]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4296]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4297]='*16. Saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo saññojaniyassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4298]='*Asaññojaniyo abyākato dhammo asaññojaniyassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4299]='*17. Hetuyā  cattāri, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā cattāri…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4300]='*Paccanīyuddhāro*';
P_HTM[4301]='*18. Saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo saññojaniyassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… sahajātapaccayena paccayo… upanissayapaccayena paccayo… purejātapaccayena paccayo… pacchājātapaccayena  paccayo… āhārapaccayena paccayo… indriyapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4302]='*19. Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4303]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4304]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4305]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4306]='*22-1. Saññojanasampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4307]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4308]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4309]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4310]='*20. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4311]='*Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4312]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4313]='*21. Saññojanasampayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanasampayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4314]='*Saññojanasampayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanasampayutto  akusalo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4315]='*22. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe pañca, adhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ, anulomaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4316]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4317]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4318]='*23. Saññojanasampayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanasampayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – vicikicchāsahagate khandhe paṭicca vicikicchāsahagato moho. Saññojanasampayuttaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – uddhaccasahagate khandhe paṭicca uddhaccasahagato moho. (2) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4319]='*24. Nahetuyā dve, naadhipatiyā pañca, napurejāte pañca…pe… nakamme tīṇi…pe… navippayutte pañca (saṃkhittaṃ, paccanīyaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4320]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[4321]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4322]='*25. Saññojanasampayutto akusalo dhammo saññojanasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4323]='*Saññojanavippayutto akusalo dhammo saññojanasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[4324]='*Saññojanasampayutto akusalo dhammo saññojanasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… nava.*';
P_HTM[4325]='*Saññojanasampayutto  akusalo dhammo saññojanasampayuttassa akusalassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4326]='*26. Adhipatiyā  ekaṃ, anantare samanantare nava, sahajāte pañca, upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, magge tīṇi, sampayutte pañca, atthiyā pañca. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4327]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[4328]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4329]='*27. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4330]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4331]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4332]='*23-1. Saññojanasaññojaniyaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4333]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4334]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4335]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4336]='*28. Saññojaniyañceva no ca saññojanaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo ceva no ca saññojano kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4337]='*29. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4338]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4339]='*30. Saññojanañceva  saññojaniyañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojano ceva saññojaniyo ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4340]='*31. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… avigate  nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4341]='*Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4342]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā.)*';
P_HTM[4343]='*32. Saññojano  ceva saññojaniyo ca akusalo dhammo saññojanassa ceva saññojaniyassa ca akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4344]='*33. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme āhāre indriye jhāne tīṇi, magge sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4345]='*34. Nahetuyā nava naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4346]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4347]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4348]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4349]='*35. Saññojaniyañceva no ca saññojanaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojaniyo ceva no ca saññojano abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā  (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4350]='*36. Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4351]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4352]='*24-1. Saññojanasaññojanasampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4353]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4354]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4355]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4356]='*37. Saññojanañceva saññojanasampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojano ceva saññojanasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4357]='*Saññojanasampayuttañceva no ca saññojanaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanasampayutto ceva no ca saññojano akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4358]='*Saññojanañceva  saññojanasampayuttaṃ akusalañca saññojanasampayuttañceva no ca saññojanaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojano ceva saññojanasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4359]='*38. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4360]='*Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4361]='*(Sahajātavāropi… sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4362]='*39. Saññojano  ceva saññojanasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo saññojanassa ceva saññojanasampayuttassa ca akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4363]='*40. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme āhāre indriye jhāne tīṇi, magge sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4364]='*41. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava, naadhipatiyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4365]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4366]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4367]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4368]='*25-1. Saññojanavippayuttasaññojaniyaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[4369]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[4370]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4371]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4372]='*42. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ saññojaniyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4373]='*Saññojanavippayuttaṃ  asaññojaniyaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto asaññojaniyo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4374]='*43. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4375]='*(Yathā cūḷantaraduke lokiyadukasadisaṃ. Sahajātavāropi…pe… pañhāvāropi sabbattha vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4376]='*44. Saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo akusalo dhammo saññojanavippayuttassa saññojaniyassa akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4377]='*45. Ārammaṇe ekaṃ (sabbattha ekaṃ, saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4378]='*46. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ saññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[4379]='*Saññojanavippayuttaṃ asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto asaññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Saññojanavippayuttaṃ asaññojaniyaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo abyākato ca saññojanavippayutto asaññojaniyo abyākato ca dhammā uppajjanti  hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[4380]='*Saññojanavippayuttaṃ saññojaniyaṃ abyākatañca saññojanavippayuttaṃ asaññojaniyaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4381]='*47. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… āsevane ekaṃ, kamme pañca, vipāke pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4382]='*Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā dve, napurejāte cattāri, napacchājāte pañca, naāsevane pañca, nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke ekaṃ, navippayutte dve…pe… novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4383]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā.)*';
P_HTM[4384]='*48. Saññojanavippayutto saññojaniyo abyākato dhammo saññojanavippayuttassa saññojaniyassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4385]='*49. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā cattāri, anantare cattāri…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4386]='*50. Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4387]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4388]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4389]='*(Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4390]='*Saññojanagocchakakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
