P_HTM[4393]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[4394]='*1. Noganthaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nogantho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4395]='*2. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4396]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4397]='*3. Ganthaṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca gantho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Ganthaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nogantho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Ganthaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca gantho akusalo ca nogantho akusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[4398]='*Noganthaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nogantho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[4399]='*Ganthaṃ akusalañca noganthaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca gantho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4400]='*4. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4401]='*Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4402]='*(Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi paṭiccavārasadisā vitthāretabbā.)*';
P_HTM[4403]='*5. Gantho akusalo dhammo ganthassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4404]='*6. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… kamme āhāre indriye jhāne tīṇi…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4405]='*7. Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4406]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4407]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4408]='*(Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4409]='*8. Noganthaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nogantho abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4410]='*9. Hetuyā  ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
