P_HTM[4510]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4511]='*1. Nonīvaraṇaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nonīvaraṇo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4512]='*2. Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4513]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4514]='*3. Nīvaraṇaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nīvaraṇaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nonīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nīvaraṇaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca  nīvaraṇo akusalo ca nonīvaraṇo akusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4515]='*4. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4516]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[4517]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[4518]='*5. Nīvaraṇaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – vicikicchānīvaraṇaṃ uddhaccanīvaraṇaṃ paṭicca avijjānīvaraṇaṃ. (1)*';
P_HTM[4519]='*Nonīvaraṇaṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – vicikicchāsahagate uddhaccasahagate khandhe paṭicca avijjānīvaraṇaṃ. (1)*';
P_HTM[4520]='*Nīvaraṇañca  nonīvaraṇañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – vicikicchānīvaraṇañca uddhaccanīvaraṇañca sampayuttake ca khandhe paṭicca avijjānīvaraṇaṃ. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[4521]='*6. Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava, napurejāte nava…pe… nakamme tīṇi…pe… navippayutte nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4522]='*(Sahajātavārepi… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha nava.)*';
P_HTM[4523]='*7. Nīvaraṇo akusalo dhammo nīvaraṇassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4524]='*8. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… āsevane nava, kamme āhāre indriye jhāne magge tīṇi, sampayutte nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4525]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4526]='*Hetupaccayā  naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4527]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4528]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[4529]='*9. Nonīvaraṇaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nonīvaraṇo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
