P_HTM[5020]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5021]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[5022]='*26. Upādānañceva upādānasampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca upādāno ceva upādānasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5023]='*Upādānasampayuttañceva no ca upādānaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ  paṭicca upādānasampayutto ceva no ca upādāno akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5024]='*Upādānañceva upādānasampayuttaṃ akusalañca upādānasampayuttañceva no ca upādānaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca upādāno ceva upādānasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5025]='*27. Hetuyā  nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ). (Imaṃ gamanaṃ upādānadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Idha pana hetupaccayā idaṃ nānaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha nava.)*';
