P_HTM[5097]='*79-1. Saṃkilesasaṃkilesikaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5098]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5099]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5100]='*20. Saṃkilesikañceva  no ca kilesaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saṃkilesiko ceva no ca kileso kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5101]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5102]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5103]='*21. Kilesañceva  saṃkilesikañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva saṃkilesiko ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5104]='*Saṃkilesikañceva no ca kilesaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saṃkilesiko ceva no ca kileso akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5105]='*Kilesañceva saṃkilesikaṃ akusalañca saṃkilesikañceva no ca kilesaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva saṃkilesiko ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5106]='*22. Hetuyā  nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ, kilesadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5107]='*23. Saṃkilesikañceva no ca kilesaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saṃkilesiko ceva no ca kileso abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5108]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5109]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5110]='*80-1. Kilesasaṃkiliṭṭhaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5111]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5112]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5113]='*24. Kilesañceva  saṃkiliṭṭhañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva saṃkiliṭṭho ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5114]='*Saṃkiliṭṭhañceva no ca kilesaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca saṃkiliṭṭho ceva no ca kileso akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5115]='*Kilesañceva saṃkiliṭṭhaṃ akusalañca saṃkiliṭṭhañceva no ca kilesaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva saṃkiliṭṭho ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5116]='*25. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ. Kilesadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārampi…pe… pañhāvārampi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5117]='*81-1. Kilesakilesasampayuttaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5118]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5119]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5120]='*26. Kilesañceva kilesasampayuttañca akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva kilesasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5121]='*Kilesasampayuttañceva  no ca kilesaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca  kilesasampayutto ceva no ca kileso akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5122]='*Kilesañceva kilesasampayuttaṃ akusalañca kilesasampayuttañceva no ca kilesaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca kileso ceva kilesasampayutto ca akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5123]='*27. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ. Kilesadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5124]='*82-1. Kilesavippayuttasaṃkilesikaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5125]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5126]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5127]='*28. Kilesavippayuttaṃ saṃkilesikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kilesavippayutto saṃkilesiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5128]='*Kilesavippayuttaṃ asaṃkilesikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kilesavippayutto asaṃkilesiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5129]='*29. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ. Lokiyadukakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5130]='*30. Kilesavippayuttaṃ  saṃkilesikaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kilesavippayutto saṃkilesiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5131]='*Kilesavippayuttaṃ  asaṃkilesikaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kilesavippayutto asaṃkilesiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5132]='*Kilesavippayuttaṃ  saṃkilesikaṃ abyākatañca kilesavippayuttaṃ asaṃkilesikaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca kilesavippayutto saṃkilesiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5133]='*31. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe… āsevane ekaṃ…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ. Lokiyadukaabyākatasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5134]='*Kilesagocchakakusalattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[5135]='*83-1. Dassanenapahātabbaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5136]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5137]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5138]='*1. Nadassanena pahātabbaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5139]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ, adhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5140]='*2. Dassanena  pahātabbaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5141]='*Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve, adhipatiyā dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5142]='*3. Dassanena pahātabbaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbo akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā – vicikicchāsahagate khandhe paṭicca vicikicchāsahagato moho. (1)*';
P_HTM[5143]='*Nadassanena pahātabbaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbo akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5144]='*4. Nahetuyā dve, naadhipatiyā dve, napurejāte dve…pe… nakamme dve, navipāke dve, navippayutte dve (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… sampayuttavārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5145]='*5. Dassanena  pahātabbo akusalo dhammo dassanena pahātabbassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5146]='*Nadassanena pahātabbo akusalo dhammo nadassanena pahātabbassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5147]='*6. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe tīṇi (dassane ekaṃ, nadassane dve), adhipatiyā tīṇi (dassanena pahātabbamūlakaṃ ekaṃ, nadassane dve, ārammaṇādhipati, sahajātādhipati, ekārammaṇādhipati), anantare dve (dassanamūlakaṃ ekaṃ, nadassane ekaṃ), samanantare dve, sahajāte dve…pe… upanissaye tīṇi, āsevane dve, kamme dve, āhāre dve…pe… sampayutte dve, atthiyā dve, natthiyā dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5148]='*7. Nadassanena pahātabbaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5149]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5150]='*(Sahajātavārepi …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5151]='*84-1. Bhāvanāyapahātabbaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5152]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5153]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5154]='*8. Nabhāvanāya pahātabbaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabhāvanāya pahātabbo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5155]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5156]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5157]='*9. Bhāvanāya pahātabbaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca bhāvanāya pahātabbo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5158]='*Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ. Dassanena pahātabbadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi  …pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5159]='*10. Nabhāvanāya  pahātabbaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabhāvanāya pahātabbo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5160]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5161]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5162]='*85-1. Dassanenapahātabbahetukaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5163]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5164]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5165]='*11. Nadassanena  pahātabbahetukaṃ kusalaṃ dhamma paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbahetuko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5166]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5167]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5168]='*12. Dassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5169]='*Nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (2)*';
P_HTM[5170]='*Dassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalañca nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5171]='*Dassanena  pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca dassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā… tīṇi (nadassane dve, ghaṭane ekaṃ, saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5172]='*13. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe cha, adhipatiyā dve (sabbattha cha), avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5173]='*14. Dassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā.*';
P_HTM[5174]='*Nadassanena  pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5175]='*15. Nahetuyā dve, naadhipatiyā cha…pe… nakamme cattāri, navipāke cha, navippayutte cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo).*';
P_HTM[5176]='*16. Dassanena pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo dassanena pahātabbahetukassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5177]='*17. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā tīṇi (dassane ekaṃ, nadassane dve), anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte cha…pe… upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme cattāri, āhāre cattāri, indriye cattāri…pe… sampayutte cha, atthiyā cha, natthiyā nava…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5178]='*18. Nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nadassanena  pahātabbahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5179]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5180]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5181]='*86-1. Bhāvanāyapahātabbahetukaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5182]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5183]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5184]='*19. Nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5185]='*Hetuyā  ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5186]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5187]='*20. Bhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca bhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5188]='*Nabhāvanāya  pahātabbahetukaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5189]='*21. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe cha, adhipatiyā dve…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Dassanena pahātabbahetukadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5190]='*22. Nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā  (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5191]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5192]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5193]='*87-1. Savitakkaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5194]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5195]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5196]='*23. Savitakkaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Savitakkaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avitakko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Savitakkaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko kusalo ca avitakko kusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[5197]='*Avitakkaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avitakko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Avitakkaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (2)*';
P_HTM[5198]='*Savitakkaṃ kusalañca avitakkaṃ kusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5199]='*24. Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe cha (sabbattha cha), avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5200]='*Naadhipatiyā cha, napurejāte cha…pe… nakamme cattāri…pe… navippayutte cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5201]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[5202]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayā*';
P_HTM[5203]='*25. Savitakko  kusalo dhammo savitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena  paccayo. Savitakko kusalo dhammo avitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. Savitakko kusalo dhammo savitakkassa kusalassa ca avitakkassa kusalassa ca dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[5204]='*Avitakko kusalo dhammo avitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5205]='*Savitakko kusalo dhammo savitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5206]='*Avitakko  kusalo dhammo avitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5207]='*Savitakko kusalo ca avitakko kusalo ca dhammā savitakkassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5208]='*26. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava (heṭṭhā tīsu sahajātādhipati, avitakke ekaṃ, sahajātādhipati), anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte cha…pe… upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme cattāri, āhāre cattāri, indriye cattāri, jhāne cha, magge cha, sampayutte cha, atthiyā cha, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5209]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5210]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5211]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5212]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5213]='*Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[5214]='*27. Savitakkaṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Savitakkaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avitakko akusalo  dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Savitakkaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo ca avitakko akusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[5215]='*Avitakkaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5216]='*Savitakkaṃ  akusalañca avitakkaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5217]='*28. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe pañca (sabbattha pañca)…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5218]='*29. Savitakkaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5219]='*Avitakkaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5220]='*Savitakkaṃ akusalañca avitakkaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5221]='*30. Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā pañca, nakamme tīṇi…pe… navippayutte pañca. (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo.)*';
P_HTM[5222]='*31. Savitakko akusalo dhammo savitakkassa akusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5223]='*32. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava…pe… sahajāte pañca…pe… upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi…pe… jhāne pañca, magge pañca, sampayutte pañca, atthiyā pañca, natthiyā nava…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5224]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[5225]='*33. Savitakkaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5226]='*Avitakkaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avitakko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5227]='*Savitakkaṃ abyākatañca avitakkaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savitakko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5228]='*34. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… purejāte āsevane cha…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5229]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… napurejāte nava…pe… nakamme cattāri, navipāke nava, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge nava, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte cha…pe… novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5230]='*35. Savitakko abyākato dhammo savitakkassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5231]='*Avitakko abyākato dhammo avitakkassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5232]='*Savitakko abyākato dhammo savitakkassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5233]='*36. Hetuyā  cattāri, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava (sabbattha nava), upanissaye nava, purejāte tīṇi, pacchājāte tīṇi, āsevane nava, kamme cattāri, vipāke nava, āhāre cattāri…pe… jhāne nava, magge nava, sampayutte cha, vippayutte pañca, atthiyā nava, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5234]='*Nahetuyā  nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5235]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5236]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5237]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5238]='*88-1. Savicāraduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5239]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5240]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5241]='*37. Savicāraṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5242]='*Avicāraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avicāro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… dve.*';
P_HTM[5243]='*Savicāraṃ kusalañca avicāraṃ kusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5244]='*38. Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe cha…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Savitakkadukakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārampi…pe… pañhāvārampi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5245]='*39. Savicāraṃ  akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5246]='*Avicāraṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5247]='*Savicāraṃ  akusalañca avicāraṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5248]='*40. Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe pañca…pe… avigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ. Savitakkadukaakusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavārampi…pe… pañhāvārampi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5249]='*41. Savicāraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5250]='*Avicāraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca avicāro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5251]='*Savicāraṃ abyākatañca avicāraṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca savicāro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5252]='*42. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… vipāke nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ. Savitakkadukaabyākatasadisaṃ. Sahajātavāropi…pe… sampayuttavāropi vitthāretabbā).*';
P_HTM[5253]='*43. Savicāro  abyākato dhammo savicārassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5254]='*44. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe nava…pe… magge cattāri  …pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5255]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5256]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5257]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5258]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5259]='*89-1. Sappītikaduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5260]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5261]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5262]='*45. Sappītikaṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sappītikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appītiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sappītikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko kusalo ca appītiko kusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[5263]='*Appītikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appītiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Appītikaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (2)*';
P_HTM[5264]='*Sappītikaṃ kusalañca appītikaṃ kusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5265]='*46. Hetuyā cha (sabbattha cha)…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5266]='*Naadhipatiyā cha, napurejāte cha…pe… nakamme cattāri, navippayutte cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārampi  …pe… sampayuttavārampi vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5267]='*47. Sappītiko kusalo dhammo sappītikassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5268]='*Appītiko  kusalo dhammo appītikassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5269]='*Sappītiko kusalo dhammo sappītikassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5270]='*48. Hetuyā  cattāri, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava (cattāri sahajātādhipati), anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte cha…pe… upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme cattāri, āhāre cattāri, indriye cattāri, jhāne cha, magge cattāri, sampayutte cha, atthiyā cha, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5271]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5272]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5273]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5274]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5275]='*Akusalapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[5276]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[5277]='*49. Sappītikaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5278]='*Appītikaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appītiko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… dve.*';
P_HTM[5279]='*Sappītikaṃ akusalañca appītikaṃ akusalañca dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5280]='*50. Hetuyā  cha, ārammaṇe cha…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Kusalasadisaṃ. Sahajātavāropi…pe… pañhāvāropi vitthāretabbā).*';
P_HTM[5281]='*Abyākatapadaṃ*';
P_HTM[5282]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[5283]='*51. Sappītikaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5284]='*Appītikaṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca appītiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5285]='*Sappītikaṃ  abyākatañca appītikaṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca sappītiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5286]='*52. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe… purejāte cha, āsevane cha…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5287]='*Nahetuyā nava, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… nakamme cattāri, navipāke nava, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge nava, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte cha…pe… (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo).*';
P_HTM[5288]='*53. Sappītiko abyākato dhammo sappītikassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5289]='*54. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava…pe… (sabbattha nava), upanissaye nava, purejāte tīṇi, pacchājāte tīṇi, āsevane nava, kamme cattāri, vipāke nava, āhāre cattāri, indriye cattāri, jhāne nava, magge cattāri, sampayutte cha, vippayutte pañca, atthiyā nava…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5290]='*90-91-1. Pītisahagatādiduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5291]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5292]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5293]='*55. Pītisahagataṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…. (Kusalampi akusalampi abyākatampi sappītikadukasadisaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5294]='*56. Sukhasahagataṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…. (Kusalampi akusalampi abyākatampi sappītikadukasadisaṃ. Akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe… paccanīye nahetuyā ekaṃ. Abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe… paccanīye nahetuyā nava…pe… najhāne cha, kātabbā. Paccanīye pañhāvāre kusalākusale indriye jhāne cha, pañhāvāre abyākate nava).*';
P_HTM[5295]='*92-1. Upekkhāsahagataduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5296]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5297]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5298]='*57. Upekkhāsahagataṃ  kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe… cha (sappītikadukasadisaṃ, upekkhāti nānāupekkhā abyākate. Paccanīye nahetuyā nava, najhāne cha).*';
P_HTM[5299]='*58. Upekkhāsahagataṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca upekkhāsahagato akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5300]='*Hetuyā cha (sabbattha cha. Saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5301]='*59. Upekkhāsahagataṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca upekkhāsahagato akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5302]='*Naupekkhāsahagataṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ  paṭicca upekkhāsahagato akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5303]='*Upekkhāsahagatañca naupekkhāsahagatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca upekkhāsahagato akusalo dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5304]='*60. Nahetuyā tīṇi, naadhipatiyā cha…pe… navippayutte cha (saṃkhittaṃ. Evaṃ sabbattha akusalaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ. Sappītikadukasadisaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5305]='*61. Upekkhāsahagataṃ  abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca upekkhāsahagato abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā nava pañhā (sappītikadukaabyākatasadisaṃ. Pañhāvāre kusalākusale indriye jhāne cha, abyākate nava).*';
P_HTM[5306]='*93-1. Kāmāvacaraduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5307]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5308]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5309]='*62. Kāmāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kāmāvacaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5310]='*Nakāmāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nakāmāvacaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5311]='*63. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe dve (sabbattha dve), avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5312]='*Naadhipatiyā dve…pe… navippayutte dve. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5313]='*(Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo.)*';
P_HTM[5314]='*64. Kāmāvacaro kusalo dhammo kāmāvacarassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5315]='*Nakāmāvacaro kusalo dhammo nakāmāvacarassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5316]='*65. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā tīṇi (kāmāvacare ekaṃ, nakāmāvacare dve), anantare tīṇi (kāmāvacare dve, nakāmāvacare ekaṃ)…pe… sahajāte dve …pe… upanissaye cattāri, āsevane tīṇi, kamme dve, āhāre dve…pe… natthiyā tīṇi…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5317]='*66. Kāmāvacaraṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kāmāvacaro akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5318]='*Hetuyā ekaṃ, ārammaṇe ekaṃ…pe… avigate ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5319]='*(Sahajātavārepi…pe… pañhāvārepi sabbattha ekaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5320]='*67. Kāmāvacaraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kāmāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5321]='*Nakāmāvacaraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nakāmāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5322]='*Kāmāvacaraṃ abyākatañca nakāmāvacaraṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca kāmāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5323]='*68. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… aññamaññe cha…pe… purejāte dve, āsevane dve…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5324]='*Nahetuyā  ekaṃ, naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā nava…pe… nakamme dve, navipāke pañca, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte tīṇi, navippayutte dve, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo).*';
P_HTM[5325]='*69. Kāmāvacaro  abyākato dhammo kāmāvacarassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5326]='*Nakāmāvacaro  abyākato dhammo nakāmāvacarassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5327]='*70. Hetuyā cattāri, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā cattāri (kāmāvacare ekaṃ, nakāmāvacare tīṇi, kāmāvacare sahajātādhipatiyeva), anantare cattāri, samanantare cattāri, sahajāte satta, aññamaññe cha, nissaye satta, upanissaye cattāri, purejāte dve, pacchājāte dve, āsevane tīṇi, kamme cattāri, vipāke cattāri, āhāre cattāri…pe… sampayutte dve, vippayutte tīṇi, atthiyā satta, natthiyā cattāri…pe… avigate satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5328]='*94-1. Rūpāvacaraduka-kusalattikaṃ*';
P_HTM[5329]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[5330]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[5331]='*71. Rūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca rūpāvacaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[5332]='*Narūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5333]='*72. Hetuyā dve, ārammaṇe dve (sabbattha dve, saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5334]='*Naadhipatiyā dve…pe… napurejāte ekaṃ, naāsevane ekaṃ…pe… navippayutte ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ. Sahajātavārādi vitthāretabbo).*';
P_HTM[5335]='*73. Rūpāvacaro  kusalo dhammo rūpāvacarassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[5336]='*Narūpāvacaro  kusalo dhammo narūpāvacarassa kusalassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[5337]='*74. Hetuyā  dve, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā tīṇi (rūpāvacare ekaṃ, sahajātādhipatiyeva, narūpāvacare dve), anantare tīṇi (rūpāvacare ekaṃ, narūpāvacare dve), samanantare tīṇi, sahajāte dve…pe… upanissaye cattāri, āsevane tīṇi, kamme dve…pe… atthiyā dve, natthiyā tīṇi…pe… avigate dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5338]='*75. Narūpāvacaraṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā (sabbattha ekaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5339]='*Rūpāvacaraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca rūpāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5340]='*Narūpāvacaraṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[5341]='*Rūpāvacaraṃ abyākatañca narūpāvacaraṃ abyākatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca rūpāvacaro abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[5342]='*76. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā pañca…pe… purejāte āsevane dve…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ. Yathā kāmāvacaradukaabyākatasadisaṃ, ettakāyeva pañhā heṭṭhuparikaṃ parivattanti. Sahajātavārampi…pe… pañhāvārampi sabbattha vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
