P_HTM[6300]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6301]='*(Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
