P_HTM[6305]='*Asekkho  nahetu dhammo nevasekkhanāsekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6306]='*Nevasekkhanāsekkho nahetu dhammo nevasekkhanāsekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Nevasekkhanāsekkho nahetu dhammo sekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Nevasekkhanāsekkho nahetu dhammo asekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6307]='*Sekkho nahetu dhammo sekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
