P_HTM[6309]='*Nevasekkhanāsekkho nahetu dhammo nevasekkhanāsekkhassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6310]='*157. Ārammaṇe pañca, adhipatiyā nava, anantare aṭṭha, samanantare aṭṭha, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe tīṇi, nissaye terasa, upanissaye aṭṭha…pe… avigate terasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
