P_HTM[6411]='*Ārammaṇapaccayā nahetuyā satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6412]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6413]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6414]='*14-1. Hīnattika-hetudukaṃ*';
P_HTM[6415]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[6416]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6417]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6418]='*174. Hīnaṃ  hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hīno hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Majjhimaṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca majjhimo hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Paṇītaṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca paṇīto hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6419]='*175. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe tīṇi…pe… avigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6420]='*Naadhipatiyā tīṇi, napurejāte tīṇi, napacchājāte tīṇi, naāsevane tīṇi, navipāke tīṇi, navippayutte tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6421]='*(Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6422]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayā*';
P_HTM[6423]='*176. Hīno hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6424]='*Majjhimo hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6425]='*Paṇīto hetu dhammo paṇītassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6426]='*Hīno hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Hīno hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6427]='*Majjhimo  hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Majjhimo hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6428]='*Paṇīto hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6429]='*177. Hīno  hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6430]='*Majjhimo hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Majjhimo hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6431]='*Paṇīto hetu dhammo paṇītassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Paṇīto hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6432]='*Hīno hetu dhammo hīnassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… dve.*';
P_HTM[6433]='*Majjhimo hetu dhammo majjhimassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… dve.*';
P_HTM[6434]='*Paṇīto hetu dhammo paṇītassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6435]='*178. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe pañca, adhipatiyā pañca…pe. … avigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6436]='*Nahetuyā aṭṭha, naārammaṇe aṭṭha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6437]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6438]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6439]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6440]='*Nahetupadaṃ*';
P_HTM[6441]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6442]='*179. Hīnaṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hīno nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.*';
P_HTM[6443]='*(Yathā saṃkiliṭṭhattikahetudukaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6444]='*15-1. Micchattaniyatattika-hetudukaṃ*';
P_HTM[6445]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[6446]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6447]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6448]='*180. Micchattaniyataṃ  hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca micchattaniyato hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[6449]='*Sammattaniyataṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sammattaniyato hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[6450]='*Aniyataṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6451]='*181. Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā tīṇi…pe… vipāke ekaṃ…pe… avigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6452]='*Naadhipatiyā dve, napurejāte dve, napacchājāte tīṇi, naāsevane ekaṃ, navipāke tīṇi, navippayutte dve (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6453]='*(Sahajātavārampi  …pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6454]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayādi*';
P_HTM[6455]='*182. Micchattaniyato  hetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6456]='*Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6457]='*Aniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6458]='*Micchattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6459]='*Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6460]='*Aniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6461]='*Aniyato  hetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6462]='*Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6463]='*Aniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6464]='*Anantarapaccayādi*';
P_HTM[6465]='*183. Micchattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6466]='*Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6467]='*Aniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato hetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato hetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6468]='*184. Micchattaniyato  hetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. Micchattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6469]='*Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. Sammattaniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6470]='*Aniyato hetu dhammo aniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato hetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato hetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa hetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6471]='*185. Hetuyā  tīṇi, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare pañca, samanantare pañca, sahajāte tīṇi…pe… upanissaye satta…pe… avigate tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6472]='*Nahetuyā satta, naārammaṇe satta (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6473]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6474]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe cattāri (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6475]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6476]='*Nahetupadaṃ*';
P_HTM[6477]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[6478]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6479]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6480]='*186. Micchattaniyataṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca micchattaniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6481]='*Sammattaniyataṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sammattaniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sammattaniyataṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Sammattaniyataṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sammattaniyato nahetu ca aniyato nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[6482]='*Aniyataṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[6483]='*Micchattaniyataṃ nahetuñca aniyataṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[6484]='*Sammattaniyataṃ nahetuñca aniyataṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6485]='*187. Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā nava…pe… vipāke ekaṃ…pe… avigate nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6486]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[6487]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6488]='*188. Aniyataṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca aniyato nahetu dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6489]='*Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā tīṇi…pe… novigate pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6490]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6491]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6492]='*(Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6493]='*Ārammaṇa-adhipati-anantarapaccayā*';
P_HTM[6494]='*189. Micchattaniyato nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6495]='*Sammattaniyato nahetu dhammo  aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6496]='*Aniyato nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato nahetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato nahetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6497]='*190. Micchattaniyato nahetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6498]='*Sammattaniyato nahetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Sammattaniyato  nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Sammattaniyato nahetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa nahetussa ca aniyatassa nahetussa ca dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6499]='*Aniyato  nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Aniyato nahetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6500]='*Micchattaniyato nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6501]='*Sammattaniyato nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (1)*';
P_HTM[6502]='*Aniyato nahetu dhammo aniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato nahetu dhammo micchattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Aniyato nahetu dhammo sammattaniyatassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6503]='*191. Ārammaṇe  pañca, adhipatiyā aṭṭha, anantare pañca, samanantare pañca, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe tīṇi, nissaye terasa, upanissaye satta…pe… avigate terasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6504]='*Nahetuyā terasa, naārammaṇe terasa, naadhipatiyā terasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6505]='*Ārammaṇapaccayā nahetuyā pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6506]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6507]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6508]='*16-1. Maggārammaṇattika-hetudukaṃ*';
P_HTM[6509]='*1-7. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[6510]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6511]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6512]='*192. Maggārammaṇaṃ  hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6513]='*Maggahetukaṃ  hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6514]='*Maggādhipatiṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipati hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6515]='*Maggārammaṇaṃ hetuñca maggādhipatiṃ hetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6516]='*Maggahetukaṃ hetuñca maggādhipatiṃ hetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko hetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6517]='*193. Hetuyā sattarasa…pe… avigate sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6518]='*Naadhipatiyā  sattarasa, napurejāte sattarasa…pe… naāsevane nava, navipāke sattarasa, navippayutte sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6519]='*(Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6520]='*Hetu-ārammaṇapaccayādi*';
P_HTM[6521]='*194. Maggārammaṇo hetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6522]='*Maggahetuko  hetu dhammo maggahetukassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6523]='*Maggādhipati hetu dhammo maggādhipatissa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6524]='*Maggārammaṇo hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6525]='*Maggahetuko hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggahetukassa hetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6526]='*Maggahetuko hetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko hetu dhammo maggādhipatissa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko hetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa hetussa ca maggādhipatissa hetussa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6527]='*Maggādhipati  hetu dhammo maggādhipatissa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6528]='*Maggahetuko hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6529]='*195. Maggārammaṇo hetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6530]='*Maggahetuko hetu dhammo  maggahetukassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6531]='*Maggādhipati hetu dhammo maggādhipatissa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6532]='*Maggārammaṇo  hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6533]='*Maggahetuko hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6534]='*Maggārammaṇo hetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6535]='*Maggādhipati hetu dhammo maggādhipatissa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6536]='*Maggārammaṇo hetu ca maggādhipati hetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa hetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6537]='*196. Hetuyā sattarasa, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā ekavīsa, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte sattarasa, aññamaññe sattarasa, nissaye sattarasa, upanissaye ekavīsa…pe… avigate sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6538]='*Nahetuyā ekavīsa, naārammaṇe sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6539]='*Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6540]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6541]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6542]='*Nahetupadaṃ*';
P_HTM[6543]='*1-6. Paṭiccavārādi*';
P_HTM[6544]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6545]='*Hetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6546]='*197. Maggārammaṇaṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggārammaṇaṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipati nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggārammaṇaṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[6547]='*Maggahetukaṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggahetukaṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipati nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggahetukaṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[6548]='*Maggādhipati nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipati nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggādhipatiṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggādhipatiṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggādhipatiṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. Maggādhipatiṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (5)*';
P_HTM[6549]='*Maggārammaṇaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggārammaṇaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipati  nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggārammaṇaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[6550]='*Maggahetukaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggahetukaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggādhipatiṃ nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Maggahetukaṃ nahetuñca maggādhipatiṃ nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6551]='*198. Hetuyā  sattarasa, ārammaṇe sattarasa…pe… avigate sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6552]='*Paccanīyaṃ*';
P_HTM[6553]='*Nahetupaccayo*';
P_HTM[6554]='*199. Maggārammaṇaṃ  nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo uppajjati nahetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6555]='*Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naadhipatiyā sattarasa, napurejāte sattarasa, napacchājāte sattarasa, naāsevane nava, navipāke sattarasa, navippayutte sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6556]='*Hetupaccayā naadhipatiyā sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6557]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6558]='*(Sahajātavārampi…pe… sampayuttavārampi paṭiccavārasadisaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6559]='*Nahetupadaṃ*';
P_HTM[6560]='*7. Pañhāvāro*';
P_HTM[6561]='*Paccayacatukkaṃ*';
P_HTM[6562]='*Ārammaṇapaccayādi*';
P_HTM[6563]='*200. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa  ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6564]='*Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6565]='*Maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6566]='*201. Maggārammaṇo  nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6567]='*Maggahetuko  nahetu dhammo maggahetukassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. Maggahetuko nahetu dhammo maggahetukassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo. (5)*';
P_HTM[6568]='*Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6569]='*Maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6570]='*Maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggahetukassa nahetussa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6571]='*Anantara-upanissayapaccayā*';
P_HTM[6572]='*202. Maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Maggārammaṇo  nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6573]='*Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa ca maggādhipatissa nahetussa ca dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo. (3)*';
P_HTM[6574]='*Maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa anantarapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi…pe….*';
P_HTM[6575]='*203. Maggārammaṇo nahetu dhammo maggārammaṇassa nahetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6576]='*Maggahetuko  nahetu dhammo maggahetukassa nahetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6577]='*Maggādhipati nahetu dhammo maggādhipatissa nahetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo… pañca.*';
P_HTM[6578]='*Maggārammaṇo nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggārammaṇassa nahetussa  dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[6579]='*Maggahetuko nahetu ca maggādhipati nahetu ca dhammā maggahetukassa nahetussa dhammassa upanissayapaccayena paccayo… pañca (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6580]='*204. Ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā ekavīsa, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte sattarasa, aññamaññe sattarasa, nissaye sattarasa, upanissaye ekavīsa…pe… avigate sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6581]='*Nahetuyā ekavīsa, naārammaṇe sattarasa (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6582]='*Ārammaṇapaccayā nahetuyā nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6583]='*Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe nava (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6584]='*(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)*';
