P_HTM[6684]='*Ajjhatto hetu dhammo ajjhattassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Ajjhatto hetu dhammo bahiddhā hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
P_HTM[6685]='*Bahiddhā  hetu dhammo bahiddhā hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Bahiddhā hetu dhammo ajjhattassa hetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2)*';
