P_HTM[6706]='*Bahiddhā nahetu dhammo bahiddhā nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Bahiddhā nahetu dhammo ajjhattassa nahetussa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (2) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
P_HTM[6707]='*230. Ārammaṇe  cattāri, adhipatiyā cattāri, anantare dve  …pe… upanissaye cattāri…pe… avigate cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[6708]='*Nahetuyā cha, naārammaṇe cha (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
