P_HTM[7152]='*41. Kusalaṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kusalo kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kusalaṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Kusalaṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kusalo kenaci viññeyyo ca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)*';
P_HTM[7153]='*Akusalaṃ  kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca akusalo kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… tīṇi.*';
P_HTM[7154]='*Abyākataṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[7155]='*Kusalaṃ kenaci viññeyyañca abyākataṃ kenaci viññeyyañca dhammaṃ paṭicca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[7156]='*Akusalaṃ  kenaci viññeyyañca abyākataṃ kenaci viññeyyañca dhammaṃ paṭicca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[7157]='*42. Kusalaṃ  kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca kusalo kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[7158]='*Akusalaṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca akusalo kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā. (1)*';
P_HTM[7159]='*Abyākataṃ kenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca abyākato kenaci viññeyyo dhammo uppajjati ārammaṇapaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)*';
