P_HTM[7195]='*Kusalo noāsavo dhammo kusalassa noāsavassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo (saṃkhittaṃ).*';
P_HTM[7196]='*6. Hetuyā  satta, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā dasa…pe… avigate terasa (saṃkhittaṃ. Yathā  kusalattike pañhāvāraṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ).*';
